1
00:00:16,860 --> 00:00:20,820
♪One day,
in the middle of the night at eight♪

2
00:00:20,980 --> 00:00:23,940
♪The first time that we met
in the city of stars♪

3
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:27,540
♪You sat there right apart
and I wonder how it could go this well♪

4
00:00:28,060 --> 00:00:31,940
♪Now I'm nearly closer,
more than anyone else♪

5
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:34,940
♪But just a minute later,
we became further apart♪

6
00:00:35,340 --> 00:00:38,900
♪It's just back to the start
like I'm never gonna see you again♪

7
00:00:39,140 --> 00:00:41,780
♪'Cause I know all these♪

8
00:00:41,820 --> 00:00:44,540
♪Made you overwhelmed♪

9
00:00:44,860 --> 00:00:49,900
♪And I wish I could change
the way it used to be♪

10
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:54,260
♪One day,
I hope you're gonna hear my name♪

11
00:00:54,340 --> 00:00:58,580
♪Like the song you always play
in the city bars and your shiny cars♪

12
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:01,340
♪I hope that I would see you again♪

13
00:01:01,460 --> 00:01:05,300
♪And one day,
I hope you're gonna call out my name♪

14
00:01:05,580 --> 00:01:08,660
♪Like the moment when you said
this love's gonna last♪

15
00:01:08,860 --> 00:01:11,780
♪Forever in your heart say you'll never
gonna forget all about that day♪

16
00:01:11,780 --> 00:01:16,460
=Confess Your Love=

17
00:01:16,460 --> 00:01:19,460
=Episode 24=

18
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:25,840
I didn't expect her to leave
a ticking bomb behind.

19
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:27,160
Speak.

20
00:01:27,160 --> 00:01:28,440
What is inside?

21
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,080
Zhang Ping,

22
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:31,680
don't keep on making mistakes.

23
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:34,320
It's not important what it is.

24
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,800
The police will find out about

25
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:44,200
this phone sooner or later.

26
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,200
Why don't you

27
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,200
solve this for me?

28
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:50,800
Even if they find out something
is wrong with Liu Yan's death,

29
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:53,800
someone would have already
committed suicide to escape the crime.

30
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,600
It's just some sedative,

31
00:01:58,920 --> 00:01:59,960
no need to be afraid.

32
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:01,400
There won't be pain, just a quick death.

33
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:04,480
Wait! Did you think there is

34
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,680
only one flash drive?

35
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,360
We made backups.

36
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,120
How would I know
you're not lying to me?

37
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,400
Do you dare bet on it?

38
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:14,000
Liu Yan said it very clearly inside

39
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:16,120
that Lu Xun and I saved her.

40
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,640
There is also a photograph.

41
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:19,080
As soon as these get exposed,

42
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,880
you will pay for all that you've done now

43
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:23,080
and to Liu Yan six years ago.

44
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:25,760
I think

45
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,720
you don't have what it takes to bet.

46
00:02:31,170 --> 00:02:31,980
Curse you.

47
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:56,840
Lin Chen.

48
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,160
Where is Lin Chen?

49
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,480
With me, of course.

50
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:07,880
Lu Xun, call the police.

51
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:08,920
Don't hurt her.

52
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,200
If you don't want her dead,

53
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:14,640
then you'll bring the backup photo
and video to me.

54
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,560
I do have the backup

55
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:23,200
but you have to guarantee her safety.

56
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,400
No more tricks.

57
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:25,880
If you call the police,

58
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:28,080
then she is as good as dead.

59
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,000
Where is the item?

60
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,000
Let Lin Chen go first.

61
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,360
Do you think I'm a fool?

62
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:55,680
Let her go.

63
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:57,560
What if you gave me a fake

64
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,120
or have other backups?

65
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,240
If I hand it to you,

66
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,360
how would I know
you will let her go as promised?

67
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,280
Don't touch her.

68
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,480
Clearly,

69
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:12,040
you don't have the power to negotiate.

70
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:24,680
Buy time.

71
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:28,400
The laptop is there.

72
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,240
Play it for me.

73
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,160
If you dare lie to me,

74
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,680
both of you cannot escape.

75
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,400
Lu Xun.

76
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:51,080
Didn't I say

77
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:53,080
I would get the car with you?

78
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:54,600
But you insisted on making me
wait for you at the entrance.

79
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,320
How would I know he was outside?

80
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,920
This was also unexpected.

81
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:04,360
Then, if we survive this,

82
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:06,320
can I not pay you the money
in the contract?

83
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,520
No.

84
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:11,320
Aren't you a president?

85
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,880
Why are you always so stingy?

86
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,800
I resigned

87
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,120
so I need to save money.

88
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,160
Stop talking, hurry up.

89
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:30,080
Actually, I have had a crush on you

90
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:31,120
since high school.

91
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,680
I know.

92
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,600
It's just that you don't know.

93
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,800
Know what?

94
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:46,600
You don't know

95
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,840
that I wrote you a love letter.

96
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:55,000
You don't know

97
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,280
that I loitered around

98
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:59,480
after school every day

99
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:02,000
so I could take the same bus as you.

100
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,760
You don't know

101
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:08,520
that before you love me,

102
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,040
I've already loved you.

103
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:14,680
Loving you makes me happy

104
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:16,400
and also makes me a coward.

105
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:19,480
I worry that these six years
would be too long.

106
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,920
So long that you would've forgotten me.

107
00:06:22,960 --> 00:06:23,960
So long that

108
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,800
you would've fallen out of love with me.

109
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:29,840
Lu Xun.

110
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,760
I'm not here to listen to

111
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,880
your sappy stories.

112
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,520
Hurry up, no more tricks.

113
00:06:36,900 --> 00:06:38,700
(This folder is empty.)

114
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,840
Give it here.

115
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,920
Let me see it, turn it around.

116
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,080
You tricked me!

117
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,400
Freeze, police!

118
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,760
Get up, don't move.

119
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,200
I told you,

120
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:20,160
I am no longer that student
from six years ago.

121
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,240
You dare call the police?

122
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:23,560
Did you really think
you can threaten me?

123
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:25,680
I really have a backup.

124
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,440
You're doomed.

125
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:32,520
Zhang Ping,

126
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:35,160
we are now taking you into custody
to be investigated.

127
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:35,920
Understand?

128
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,760
No.

129
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:37,800
- I won't lose.
- Take him away.

130
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:38,720
Let me go.

131
00:07:43,820 --> 00:07:48,220
♪I've already noticed you behind me♪

132
00:07:48,860 --> 00:07:55,700
♪All you want to say
are just parting words♪

133
00:07:56,140 --> 00:07:59,180
♪Our reflections♪

134
00:07:59,420 --> 00:08:03,940
♪Are split into two different worlds♪

135
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:05,240
Lu Xun.

136
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:10,860
♪Just like clouds
waving goodbye to the sun♪

137
00:08:11,460 --> 00:08:15,340
♪I trapped my feelings
under the surface of a lake♪

138
00:08:15,700 --> 00:08:18,860
♪So you can't see my tears♪

139
00:08:18,860 --> 00:08:25,300
♪It doesn't match this vague scenery♪

140
00:08:25,580 --> 00:08:28,220
♪The warmth on your palms♪

141
00:08:28,580 --> 00:08:34,180
♪Can never be warmed by me♪

142
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:43,880
Lu Xun. Lu Xun!

143
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:45,680
How do you feel?

144
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:47,960
You...

145
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,600
Did you lose your memory?

146
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,880
Have you forgotten me?

147
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:52,200
My God, doctor!

148
00:08:58,280 --> 00:08:59,440
I was saying

149
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:00,960
were you crying?

150
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:03,480
Your injury.

151
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,480
Then, don't move.

152
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:10,780
Okay.

153
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:13,440
What I said just now

154
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,840
are all the truth.

155
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,320
You know that, right?

156
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:22,680
Then, does that mean
you confessed your love first?

157
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:25,920
Yes, I confessed first.

158
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,960
I've been wanting to tell you

159
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:30,960
that I love you.

160
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:34,120
Since I was 16 until now,

161
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,440
I love you.

162
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:37,840
Me too.

163
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:41,220
♪Where do you stop your gaze♪

164
00:09:42,020 --> 00:09:45,540
♪When my eyes meet yours,
my heart beats fast♪

165
00:09:45,700 --> 00:09:49,580
♪The scent of roses hidden
behind me engulfs us♪

166
00:09:49,740 --> 00:09:53,260
♪Turn on the starlight radio
and let my love♪

167
00:09:53,260 --> 00:09:56,180
♪Be broadcasted all across
Milky Way and beyond♪

168
00:09:56,460 --> 00:09:58,740
♪The love I'm afraid to put into words♪

169
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:07,040
I was quite worried about you.

170
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,880
Disappointed?

171
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:10,440
I am quite disappointed.

172
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:15,680
Lin Chen, come out for a moment.

173
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,640
I have something to tell you.

174
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:19,680
Say it here.

175
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:23,840
Take a rest, I'll be right back.

176
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:34,080
What is it?

177
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,160
Lin Chen,

178
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:40,600
I love you.

179
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:43,360
Are you joking again?

180
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:44,680
No.

181
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:50,880
How could I joke about this?

182
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:57,520
I've loved you

183
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,400
since high school.

184
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:03,960
The person I mentioned
at the dental clinic the last time

185
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:05,920
was you.

186
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:07,600
It had always been you.

187
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:11,880
I used to be afraid
if my confession failed,

188
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:15,920
we wouldn't be friends anymore.

189
00:11:16,920 --> 00:11:18,120
Zheng Ziyan,

190
00:11:18,640 --> 00:11:19,640
I'm sorry.

191
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:23,600
The person I love is Lu Xun.

192
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:29,080
I know but I still want to say it.

193
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,560
Because I realized

194
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:34,360
I don't want to be just your friend.

195
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:38,440
So from now onward,

196
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,840
we're not friends.

197
00:11:41,640 --> 00:11:42,960
I'm just

198
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:46,160
a person who loves you.

199
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:50,520
I'll be going abroad for training.

200
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:53,800
You don't need to contact me.

201
00:11:55,160 --> 00:11:56,840
I'll be fine on my own.

202
00:11:58,040 --> 00:11:59,880
I hope you will too.

203
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:10,320
Goodbye, Lin Chen.

204
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:17,040
Why so passionate?

205
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:21,920
What's that to you?

206
00:12:21,920 --> 00:12:24,080
Mrs. Lu's business is also my business.

207
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,640
Who is Mrs. Lu?

208
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:28,640
Have you forgotten

209
00:12:28,640 --> 00:12:30,680
what you agreed to in front of everyone?

210
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:36,400
We're getting married tomorrow.

211
00:12:38,640 --> 00:12:40,160
What are you doing?

212
00:12:41,760 --> 00:12:44,280
Lin Chen, I sent you a file.

213
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,120
Just listen to it.

214
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:56,480
You don't want him to leave?

215
00:12:56,800 --> 00:12:58,000
No.

216
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:04,120
(Voice file)
Shall we

217
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:06,280
continue what we were doing just now?

218
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:10,480
(I don't know what you've written)

219
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:13,040
(in that letter from six years ago.)

220
00:13:13,040 --> 00:13:14,160
(Why did Zheng Ziyan)

221
00:13:14,160 --> 00:13:16,320
(receive the same thing too?)

222
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:17,960
(You said)

223
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,760
(you wanted me to start hating you.)

224
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,680
My injury hurts.

225
00:13:21,680 --> 00:13:22,920
I need to rest.

226
00:13:23,520 --> 00:13:26,600
(I'm afraid that you don't love me)

227
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:28,320
(as I love you.)

228
00:13:29,680 --> 00:13:31,600
You must be Lin Wan's family, right?

229
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:33,640
You look exactly like her.

230
00:13:33,640 --> 00:13:34,520
She just woke up.

231
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:36,360
She woke up?

232
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:42,600
Lin Wan!

233
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:44,120
Lin Wan!

234
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:45,240
You're finally awake!

235
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:50,320
You're

236
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:51,680
injured.

237
00:13:51,680 --> 00:13:52,760
What happened?

238
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:56,480
Have a lot of things happened
during this period of time?

239
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:58,600
It's okay, take your time and tell me.

240
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:10,840
You're still injured.
Why do you have to take a shower?

241
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:12,440
Mind your injury, okay?

242
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,880
What's wrong? Did you fall down?

243
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,320
Are you okay?

244
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:21,880
Sorry, I'm going.

245
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:29,520
What is it?

246
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:33,240
Mrs. Lu, have you forgotten

247
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:35,080
what you haven't done today?

248
00:14:36,420 --> 00:14:39,660
♪I once wandered aimlessly at night♪

249
00:14:39,660 --> 00:14:42,740
♪The whole world seems to be against me♪

250
00:14:42,900 --> 00:14:45,940
♪You hold my hand♪

251
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:47,720
Lu Xun, what's wrong?

252
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:49,040
Are you injured again?

253
00:14:49,040 --> 00:14:50,240
Lu Xun, open up.

254
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,440
What's going on, Lu Xun?

255
00:15:00,580 --> 00:15:03,660
♪You said fate is not completely perfect♪

256
00:15:03,780 --> 00:15:06,780
♪I'm powerless against
loving or losing you♪

257
00:15:06,980 --> 00:15:09,580
♪You hold my hand and rely on me♪

258
00:15:09,580 --> 00:15:13,300
♪Calming down my anxious thoughts♪

259
00:15:13,660 --> 00:15:16,420
♪Gently wiping your tears
and pulling you into my arms♪

260
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:18,560
Lu Xun,

261
00:15:18,560 --> 00:15:19,880
you're not being

262
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:21,360
gentlemanly, are you?

263
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:23,480
Lin Chen,

264
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:26,200
I've been thinking of you
for a long time.

265
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:29,200
Can I be a gentleman during daytime?

266
00:15:30,100 --> 00:15:32,860
♪I will stand and wait for you
under the light♪

267
00:15:32,860 --> 00:15:35,100
♪Through dark corners and thorns♪

268
00:15:35,100 --> 00:15:39,300
♪Rushing towards the tenderness
only for you♪

269
00:15:39,300 --> 00:15:42,780
♪No matter how much time has passed
or how many people have left♪

270
00:15:42,780 --> 00:15:46,140
♪I keep waiting for you under the light♪

271
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:47,440
(Did you know?)

272
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:49,840
(I used to love walking by the field)

273
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:54,160
(because I could see you
standing on the rooftop.)

274
00:15:58,840 --> 00:16:00,280
(Did you know)

275
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:03,320
(why I liked to loiter on the rooftop?)

276
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:05,160
(Because you)

277
00:16:05,160 --> 00:16:07,160
(were always on the field.)

278
00:16:10,560 --> 00:16:12,560
Family and friends,

279
00:16:12,560 --> 00:16:14,640
welcome to the wedding
of Lu Xun and Lin Chen.

280
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:17,360
Now, let us welcome the bride,

281
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:19,160
Lin Chen.

282
00:16:34,860 --> 00:16:38,380
♪I take a shortcut and bump into you♪

283
00:16:38,500 --> 00:16:41,860
♪When we hold hands,
my heart goes thump-thump♪

284
00:16:41,860 --> 00:16:47,660
♪When we blow bubbles away,
they go pop-pop♪

285
00:16:47,900 --> 00:16:49,620
♪Hear my heartbeat♪

286
00:16:49,980 --> 00:16:53,620
♪We met because I took a shortcut♪

287
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:59,720
Okay, before the newlyweds
make their vows,

288
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:02,160
does anyone wish to object?

289
00:17:02,160 --> 00:17:02,840
None.

290
00:17:13,600 --> 00:17:16,000
You aren't thinking of leaving me
at the altar, are you?

291
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:17,120
You dare?

292
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:18,600
You said

293
00:17:18,600 --> 00:17:19,920
you wrote me a love letter

294
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:21,480
when you were in high school.

295
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:23,360
I have a sudden urge to know

296
00:17:23,360 --> 00:17:24,680
what was written in it.

297
00:17:26,800 --> 00:17:29,360
It happened when I was young,
I forgot.

298
00:17:30,600 --> 00:17:32,120
Then I'll have to consider this.

299
00:17:36,320 --> 00:17:38,000
It's fine if you want to know.

300
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:41,560
