301
00:17:42,320 --> 00:17:44,360
what was written
in the love letter you gave me.

302
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:54,200
Isn't this the one I gave you years ago?

303
00:17:54,200 --> 00:17:55,200
Read it.

304
00:17:58,120 --> 00:17:59,160
It's been so many years

305
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:00,480
and you still kept it.

306
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:02,520
Hurry up and just read it for us. Right?

307
00:18:02,520 --> 00:18:04,400
Yes, read it.

308
00:18:04,400 --> 00:18:06,160
Read it, read it.

309
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:12,280
Dear Schoolmate Lu Xun.

310
00:18:12,280 --> 00:18:13,560
Nice to meet you.

311
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:15,240
I am

312
00:18:15,240 --> 00:18:17,240
Lin Chen from Year 3, Class 8.

313
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:20,040
I've noticed you for a long time.

314
00:18:20,280 --> 00:18:22,520
Can you be my friend?

315
00:18:24,680 --> 00:18:26,480
I'm very good in my studies.

316
00:18:27,160 --> 00:18:28,800
We can get better at studies together.

317
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:36,720
Okay, your turn.

318
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:37,720
I wanted to ask you

319
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:39,640
if you wanted to go to a movie
with me on Saturday.

320
00:18:41,360 --> 00:18:43,680
Just that?

321
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:45,520
Just one sentence?

322
00:18:45,520 --> 00:18:46,880
You didn't say
whether you liked me or not?

323
00:18:47,280 --> 00:18:48,040
Yes.

324
00:19:05,760 --> 00:19:09,400
Lin Chen, we've been delayed
for far too long.

325
00:19:09,800 --> 00:19:11,880
I should have confessed much earlier.

326
00:19:12,560 --> 00:19:15,160
So you would know how much I love you.

327
00:19:15,180 --> 00:19:17,940
♪When I said I'm in love with you♪

328
00:19:18,100 --> 00:19:21,580
♪You didn't even seem to care♪

329
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:28,560
Meng Jiao, I love you.

330
00:19:28,660 --> 00:19:31,340
♪Maybe that's been my mistake♪

331
00:19:31,340 --> 00:19:35,340
♪You just reminded how to play♪

332
00:19:35,360 --> 00:19:36,480
If you don't love me, I'll...

333
00:19:36,660 --> 00:19:41,260
♪I need someone to take my heart♪

334
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:44,320
(If we could start all over again...)

335
00:19:46,140 --> 00:19:48,580
♪Where are you, love? I'm here for you♪

336
00:19:48,820 --> 00:19:51,340
♪I can't help it, love you too♪

337
00:19:51,360 --> 00:19:54,880
Lu Xun, for you.

338
00:19:58,040 --> 00:19:59,400
Fine, I get it!

339
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:02,240
(I would not allow this six years
to pass us by.)

340
00:20:02,300 --> 00:20:04,660
♪I need it right now♪

341
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:07,320
(I would tell you right from the start.)

342
00:20:08,880 --> 00:20:11,800
Lin Chen, I've loved you
for a long time.

343
00:20:13,380 --> 00:20:17,540
♪I need it right now♪

344
00:20:17,740 --> 00:20:21,060
♪Crying for you♪

345
00:20:28,340 --> 00:20:31,580
♪Crying for you♪

346
00:20:32,300 --> 00:20:40,060
♪Crying for you♪

347
00:20:49,460 --> 00:20:50,820
♪Crying for you♪

348
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:20,880
♪That damaged but peaceful,
little dream♪

349
00:21:21,120 --> 00:21:25,280
♪Unintentionally shines into my life
through the window♪

350
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:29,400
♪You never said it,
and I never mention it♪

351
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:32,680
♪That light, is you♪

352
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:37,760
♪Because of you, my world becomes blurry♪

353
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:41,880
♪One step forward and back,
I keep guessing your feeling♪

354
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:45,960
♪You never understood
this feelings that came out of nowhere♪

355
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:48,280
♪Under your control♪

356
00:21:48,560 --> 00:21:50,240
♪I want to say♪

357
00:21:50,520 --> 00:21:53,920
♪Will you care about
my feelings once again♪

358
00:21:54,360 --> 00:21:58,600
♪Will you let me walk on your heart
in the middle of the night♪

359
00:21:58,720 --> 00:22:01,720
♪I dare not think too much♪

360
00:22:01,840 --> 00:22:06,760
♪Or ask that you prove your love to me♪

361
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:10,880
♪Will you also hold onto your phone,
waiting for me sometimes♪

362
00:22:11,480 --> 00:22:15,560
♪Are the songs you shared about me♪

363
00:22:15,840 --> 00:22:18,800
♪I dare not say too much♪

364
00:22:18,800 --> 00:22:22,680
♪Maybe you already understand♪

365
00:22:23,120 --> 00:22:25,320
♪My heart♪

366
00:22:42,820 --> 00:22:46,940
♪Will I be the only person
in your eyes someday♪

367
00:22:47,180 --> 00:22:51,340
♪Will I be the first one you want to call
when you pick up your phone♪

368
00:22:51,580 --> 00:22:54,420
♪In my rainbow-colored starry sky♪

369
00:22:54,620 --> 00:22:59,660
♪Are all pictures of your smile♪

370
00:22:59,820 --> 00:23:03,620
♪What if you cannot dodge
any of this♪

371
00:23:04,060 --> 00:23:08,260
♪What if I'm becoming
a better version of me for you♪

372
00:23:08,500 --> 00:23:11,420
♪No need for too much words♪

